<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/shopAdd.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://dcicons.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/new/images/web/react_components/Header/logo.png" alt="다이닝코드">
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container addPage">
        
        <div class="addtitle">
            <h2>식당 추가하기</h2>
        </div>

        <form action="/add" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" >
            <div class="addForm">
                <div class="addItem">
                        <strong>음식점 이름</strong>
                        <input name="restaurantName" id="restaurantName" type="text"  placeholder="음식점 이름">
                </div>
                <div class="addItem">
                    <strong>음식점 주소</strong>
                    <input name="restaurantAddress"  id="restaurantAddress" type="text" placeholder="음식점 주소">
                </div>
                <div class="addItem">
                    <strong>영업 시간</strong>
                    <input name="openTime" id="openTime" type="text" placeholder="영업 시간">
                </div>
                <div class="addItem">
                    <strong>카테고리</strong>
                    <input name="category" id="category" type="text" placeholder="카테고리 예(파스타)">
                </div>
                <div class="addItem">
                    <strong>매장 번호</strong>
                    <input name="callNumber" id="callNumber" type="text" placeholder="전화 번호">
                </div>
                <div class="addItem">
                    <input name="imgUrl" id="imgUrl" type="file" placeholder="사진">
                </div>
                <div class="addItem">
                  <input name="views" id="views" type="hidden" value="0" placeholder="조회수">
              </div>
              
                <div class="addBtn row">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark col-4">등록하기</button>
                    <button type="reset" class="btn btn-dark col-4"><a href="/">취소하기</a></button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <!-- footer 나중에 삭제 해도 무방 -->
    <footer>
        <div class="container footerPage">
            <ul class="row row-cols-auto terms ">
                <li class="col">데이터 제휴 문의</li>
                <li class="col">개인정보처리방침</li>
                <li class="col">이용약관</li>
                <li class="col">위치기반 서비스 이용약관</li>
            </ul>
             <ul class="row row-cols-auto info">
                <li class="col fw-bolder mainName">(주)다이닝코드 </li>
                <li class="col">대표이사 : 신효섭</li>
                <li class="col">소재지 : 서울특별시 강남구 테헤란로79길 6</li>
                <li class="col">사업자등록번호 : 206-86-92418</li>
            </ul>
            <p>이메일 문의 : contact@diningcode.com</p>
            <div class="row row-cols-auto d-flex justify-content-between detailInfo">
                <span class="">전화 문의 : 02-457-1304 (평일 : 10:00 ~ 19:00, 주말/공휴일 제외)</span>
                <span class="">Copyright ⓒ 2024 Diningcode</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</html>